channel.title: Server problem for the pro's!
channel.description: OK, i'm running "Project DungeonFest 659" and he said to change my clientset to my ip? hamachi ip or no-ip ip? and where do I find my client ip? And if someone can tell me detail by detail how to make a downloadable client for my server, it doesn't upload to moparscape cause its 659. ty

item.title: Server problem for the pro's!
item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

A downloadable client, if you are referring to a cachedownloader you would just add a cachedownloader just like any server really. You would then need to make it so all paths are directed to it, and make it so it unpacks the material. Overall, not hard.

As for location of the ip…clientsettings.java if I remember correctly.
